## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not capture the full complexity of the issue. Additionally, the sources vary in their publication dates and contexts, which could affect the relevance and applicability of the information. Further research with a broader range of sources and more recent data would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the perpetuation of stereotypes in popular culture.

